                id = "0", speaker = "A Man Praying With His Back to the Death",
                text = "*(In a temple's inner sanctum, a man kneels at an altar, praying with a fervor that is almost violent in its focus — and twenty feet behind him, through the broken doors, a fading mortal form that gutters with dying divine light is *dying*, slowly, alone, and making small sounds, and the kneeling man *will not turn around.* His shoulders are rigid with the effort of not turning. He prays louder when the sounds come.)* *(without turning, hearing your step:)* If you've come to *tell* me, don't. *(his voice shakes.)* I *know* what's behind me. I have *always* known. And I am *not going to look.* So if that's your errand — *\"old man, your god is dying twenty feet away\"* — *save your breath.* I am *busy.* I am *praying.* It is the *most important* praying of my *life*, and it requires that I *face the altar*, and *not* the door.",
